<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Markfluence | Digital Marketing Pro</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }
    body {
      background-color: #0e0e0e;
      color: #f2f2f2;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    header {
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d47a1, #1976d2);
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    header p {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #111;
    }
    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #f2f2f2;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    nav a:hover {
      color: #00bcd4;
    }
    .hero {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519389950473-47ba0277781c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80') no-repeat center center/cover;
      color: white;
    }
    .hero h2 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 15px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 25px;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      background: #00bcd4;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background: #0097a7;
    }
    section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    section h3 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #00bcd4;
    }
    .services {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .card {
      background: #1e1e1e;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #333;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      background: #111;
      color: #aaa;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Markfluence</h1>
    <p>Fueling Brands with Smart Digital Strategies</p>
  </header>
  <nav>
    <a href="#services">Services</a>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>
  <section class="hero">
    <h2>Grow Your Business Online</h2>
    <p>We help brands like yours dominate digital platforms through paid ads, content marketing, and conversion optimization.</p>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn">Work With Me</a>
  </section>
  <section id="services">
    <h3>What I Do</h3>
    <div class="services">
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Social Media Ads</h4>
        <p>Run high-converting Facebook, Instagram & TikTok ads tailored to your business goals.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Funnel Building</h4>
        <p>Create sales funnels that turn visitors into loyal customers and repeat buyers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h4>Content Strategy</h4>
        <p>Design compelling content plans that position your brand as the go-to expert.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section id="about">
    <h3>About Me</h3>
    <p>I’m a digital marketer with over 5 years of experience helping startups, coaches, and small businesses scale their online presence using data-driven strategies. I combine creativity with performance marketing to deliver real business results.</p>
  </section>
  <section id="contact">
    <h3>Contact</h3>
    <p>Want to grow your business fast? Let’s work together. Reach out via WhatsApp or email today.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="https://wa.me/2349012345678" target="_blank">Message on WhatsApp</a>
  </section>
  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Markfluence. All rights reserved.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
